#: classes/settings-fields.php:443
msgid ""
"This setting determines the mode of operation for the Transliteration plugin."
msgstr "Ova postavka određuje način rada dodatka za transliteraciju."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:444
msgid ""
"Carefully choose the option that is best for your site and the plugin will "
"automatically set everything you need for optimal performance."
msgstr ""
"Pažljivo odaberite opciju koja je najbolja za vašu stranicu i dodatak će "
"automatski postaviti sve što je potrebno za optimalne performanse."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:449
msgid ""
"This section contains filters for exclusions, allowing you to specify "
"content that should be excluded from transliteration, and also includes a "
"filter to disable certain WordPress filters related to transliteration."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj odjeljak sadrži filtre za izuzeća, koji vam omogućuju da odredite "
"sadržaj koji treba biti izuzet iz transliteracije, a također uključuje "
"filtar za onemogućavanje određenih WordPress filtara povezanih s "
"transliteracijom."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:454
msgid ""
"These are special settings that can enhance transliteration and are used "
"only if you need them."
msgstr ""
"To su posebne postavke koje mogu poboljšati transliteraciju i koriste se "
"samo ako su vam potrebne."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:459
msgid "These settings apply to the administrative part."
msgstr "Ove postavke se odnose na administrativni dio."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:464
msgid "Upload, view and control media and files."
msgstr "Prenesite, pregledajte i kontrolirajte medije i datoteke."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:469
msgid ""
"Our plugin also has special SEO options that are very important for your "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Naš dodatak također ima posebne SEO opcije koje su vrlo važne za vaš projekt."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:474
msgid ""
"Within this configuration section, you have the opportunity to customize "
"your experience by selecting the particular languages for which you wish to "
"turn off the transliteration function. This feature is designed to give you "
"greater control and adaptability over how the system handles "
"transliteration, allowing you to disable it for specific languages based on "
"your individual needs or preferences."
msgstr ""
"U ovom dijelu postavki imate mogućnost prilagoditi svoje iskustvo tako da "
"odaberete određene jezike za koje želite isključiti funkciju "
"transliteracije. Ova značajka je dizajnirana kako bi vam pružila veću "
"kontrolu i prilagodljivost u načinu na koji sustav rukuje transliteracijom, "
"omogućujući vam da je isključite za određene jezike sukladno vašim osobnim "
"potrebama ili preferencijama."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:479
msgid ""
"Various interesting settings that can be used in the development of your "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Razne zanimljive postavke koje se mogu koristiti u razvoju vašeg projekta."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:487
msgid ""
"This setting determines the search mode within the WordPress core depending "
"on the type of language located in the database."
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka određuje način pretraživanja unutar jezgre WordPress-a, ovisno "
"o vrsti jezika koji se nalazi u bazi podataka."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:488
msgid ""
"The search type setting is mostly experimental and you need to test each "
"variant so you can get the best result you need."
msgstr ""
"Postavka vrste pretraživanja uglavnom je eksperimentalna i trebate testirati "
"svaku varijantu kako biste postigli najbolji rezultat koji vam je potreban."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:502 classes/utilities.php:40
msgid "Arabic"
msgstr "Arapski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:504 classes/utilities.php:39
msgid "Armenian"
msgstr "Jermenski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:520
msgid ""
"Define whether your primary alphabet on the site is Latin or Cyrillic. If "
"the primary alphabet is Cyrillic then choose Cyrillic. If it is Latin, then "
"choose Latin. This option is crucial for the plugin to work properly."
msgstr ""
"Odredite je li vaša primarna abeceda na web mjestu latinica ili ćirilica. "
"Ako je primarna abeceda ćirilica, onda odaberite ćirilicu. Ako je latinski, "
"onda odaberite latinski. Ova je opcija presudna za ispravni rad dodatka."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:522
msgid "Define whether your primary alphabet on the site."
msgstr "Odredite je li vaš primarni alfabet na stranici."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:535
msgid "Transliteration disabled"
msgstr "Transliteracija je onemogućena"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:536 classes/settings.php:692
#: classes/settings/page-shortcodes.php:8 classes/settings/page-tags.php:5
#: classes/utilities.php:1659
msgid "Cyrillic to Latin"
msgstr "Ćirilica na latinicu"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:537 classes/settings.php:693
#: classes/settings/page-shortcodes.php:14 classes/settings/page-tags.php:8
#: classes/utilities.php:1663
msgid "Latin to Cyrillic"
msgstr "Latinica na ćirilicu"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:543
msgid "Arabic to Latin"
msgstr "S arapskog na latinski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:544
msgid "Latin to Arabic"
msgstr "Latinski na arapski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:546
msgid "Armenian to Latin"
msgstr "Armenski na latinski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:547
msgid "Latin to Armenian"
msgstr "Latinski na armenski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:565
msgid ""
"This option determines the global transliteration of your web site. If you "
"do not want to transliterate the entire website and use this plugin for "
"other purposes, disable this option. This option does not affect to the "
"functionality of short codes and tags."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija određuje globalnu transliteraciju vašeg web mjesta. Ako ne želite "
"transliterirati cijelu web stranicu i koristiti ovaj dodatak u druge svrhe, "
"onemogućite ovu opciju. Ova opcija ne utječe na funkcionalnost kratkih "
"kodova i oznaka."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:585
msgid ""
"This option determines the type of language script that the visitors sees "
"when they first time come to your site."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija određuje vrstu jezične skripte koju posjetitelji vide kada prvi "
"put dođu na vašu stranicu."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:594
msgid "Automatical"
msgstr "Automatski"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:615
msgid ""
"This option defines the language script. Automatic script detection is the "
"best way but if you are using a WordPress installation in a language that "
"does not match the scripts supported by this plugin, then choose on which "
"script you want the transliteration to be performed."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija definira jezičnu skriptu. Najbolje je automatsko otkrivanje "
"skripti, ali ako koristite WordPress instalaciju na jeziku koji se ne "
"podudara sa skriptama koje podržava ovaj dodatak, odaberite na kojoj skripti "
"želite da se izvrši transliteracija."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:641
msgid ""
"This option configures the operating mode of the entire plugin and affects "
"all aspects of the site related to transliteration. Each mode has its own "
"set of filters, which are activated based on your specific needs. It's "
"important to take the time to review and customize these settings according "
"to your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija konfigurira način rada cijelog dodatka i utječe na sve aspekte "
"stranice povezane s transliteracijom. Svaki način rada ima svoj skup "
"filtera, koji se aktiviraju prema vašim specifičnim potrebama. Važno je "
"odvojiti vrijeme za pregled i prilagodbu ovih postavki u skladu s vašim "
"preferencijama."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:643
msgid ""
"Forced transliteration can sometimes cause problems if Latin is translated "
"into Cyrillic in pages and posts. To this combination must be approached "
"experimentally."
msgstr ""
"Prisilna transliteracija ponekad može stvoriti probleme ako se latinica na "
"stranicama i u postovima prevede na ćirilicu. Ovoj se kombinaciji mora "
"pristupiti eksperimentalno."

#: classes/settings-fields.php:655
msgid "Exclude filters you don't need (optional)"
msgstr "Izuzmite filtre koji vam nisu potrebni (opcionalno)"

#: classes/settings-fields.php:661
