msgstr "Postavke dodatka"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:4
msgid ""
"These are available PHP functions that you can use in your themes and "
"plugins."
msgstr ""
"Ovo su dostupne PHP funkcije koje možete koristiti u svojim temama i "
"dodacima."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:21
msgid "Determines whether the site is already in Cyrillic."
msgstr "Određuje je li stranica već na ćirilicu."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:103
msgid ""
"This function provides information on whether the currently active language "
"is excluded from transliteration."
msgstr ""
"Ova funkcija pruža informacije o tome je li trenutno aktivni jezik izuzet iz "
"transliteracije."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:107
msgid "Transliteration of some text or content into the desired script."
msgstr "Transliteracija nekog teksta ili sadržaja u željenu skriptu."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:109
msgid ""
"The <b><i>$type</i></b> parameter has two values: <code>cyr_to_lat</code> "
"(Cyrillic to Latin) and <code>lat_to_cyr</code> (Latin to Cyrillic)"
msgstr ""
"Parametar <b><i>$type</i></b> ima dvije vrijednosti: <code>cyr_to_lat</code> "
"(ćirilica na latinski) i <code>lat_to_cyr</code> (latinica na ćirilicu)"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:112
msgid "Transliteration from Cyrillic to Latin."
msgstr "Transliteracija s ćirilice na latinicu."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:116
msgid "Transliteration from Latin to Cyrillic."
msgstr "Transliteracija s latinice na ćirilicu."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:120
msgid ""
"Transliterates Cyrillic characters to Latin, converting them to their basic "
"ASCII equivalents by removing diacritics."
msgstr ""
"Transliterira ćirilične znakove u latinicu, pretvarajući ih u njihove "
"osnovne ASCII ekvivalente uklanjanjem dijakritičkih znakova."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:124
msgid "Get active script."
msgstr "Uzmite aktivnu skriptu."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:128
msgid "This function displays a selector for the transliteration script."
msgstr "Ova funkcija prikazuje odabirač za skriptu transliteracije."

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:130
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parametri"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:131
msgid ""
"This attribute contains an associative set of parameters for this function:"
msgstr "Ovaj atribut sadrži asocijativni skup parametara za ovu funkciju:"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:137
#, php-format
msgid ""
"(string) The type of selector that will be displayed on the site. It can be: "
"%1$s, %2$s, %3$s, %4$s, %5$s or %6$s. Default: %1$s"
msgstr ""
"(string) Vrsta odabirača koja će se prikazati na web-mjestu. Može biti: "
"%1$s, %2$s, %3$s, %4$s, %5$s ili %6$s. Zadano: %1$s"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:149
#, php-format
msgid ""
"(bool) determines whether it will be displayed through an echo or as a "
"string. Default: %s"
msgstr "(bool) određuje hoće li se prikazati kroz echo ili kao niz. Zadano: %s"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:154
#: classes/settings/page-shortcodes.php:52
#, php-format
msgid "(string) Separator to be used when the selector type is %s. Default: %s"
msgstr ""
"(string) Razdjelnik koji će se koristiti kada je vrsta odabirača %s. Zadano: "
"%s"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:159
#, php-format
msgid "(string) Text for Cyrillic link. Default: %s"
msgstr "(string) Tekst za ćirilični link. Zadano: %s"

#: classes/settings/page-functions.php:164
#, php-format
msgid "(string) Text for Latin link. Default: %s"
msgstr "(string) Tekst za latiničnog linka. Zadano: %s"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:2
msgid ""
"This tool enables you to convert all existing Cyrillic permalinks in your "
"database to Latin characters."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj alat omogućuje vam da pretvorite sve postojeće ćirilične permalinke u "
"vašoj bazi podataka u latinična slova."

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:4
msgid "Warning:"
msgstr "Upozorenje:"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:7
msgid ""
"This option is dangerous and can create unexpected problems. Once you run "
"this script, all permalinks in your database will be modified and this can "
"affect on the SEO causing a 404 error."
msgstr ""
"Ova je opcija opasna i može stvoriti neočekivane probleme. Jednom kada "
"pokrenete ovu skriptu, sve trajne veze u vašoj bazi podataka bit će "
"izmijenjene, a to može utjecati na SEO što uzrokuje pogrešku 404."

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:10
msgid ""
"Before proceeding, consult with your SEO specialist, as you will likely need "
"to resubmit your sitemap and adjust other settings to update the permalinks "
"in search engines."
msgstr ""
"Prije nego što nastavite, konzultirajte se sa svojim SEO stručnjakom, jer "
"ćete vjerojatno trebati ponovno poslati svoju mapu sajta i prilagoditi "
"ostale postavke kako biste ažurirali permalinke u tražilicama."

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:12
msgid ""
"For advanced users, this function can also be executed via WP-CLI using the "
"command"
msgstr ""
"Za napredne korisnike, ova funkcija se također može izvršiti putem WP-CLI "
"koristeći naredbu"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:14
#, php-format
msgid "Important: Make sure to %s before running this script."
msgstr "Važno: Provjerite da ste %s prije nego što pokrenete ovaj skript."

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:14
msgid "back up your database"
msgstr "napravite sigurnosnu kopiju svoje baze podataka"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:26
#, php-format
msgid "This tool will affect on the following post types: %s"
msgstr "Ovaj će alat utjecati na sljedeće vrste postova: %s"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:40
msgid "Let's do magic"
msgstr "Napravimo magiju"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:43
msgid "Are you sure you want this?"
msgstr "Jeste li sigurni da ovo želite?"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:47
msgid "Disclaimer"
msgstr "Odricanje od odgovornosti"

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:48
msgid ""
"While this tool is designed to operate safely, there is always a small risk "
"of unpredictable issues."
msgstr ""
"Iako je ovaj alat dizajniran da radi sigurno, uvijek postoji mali rizik od "
"nepredvidivih problema."

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:49
msgid ""
"Note: We do not guarantee that this tool will function correctly on your "
"server. By using it, you assume all risks and responsibilities for any "
"potential issues."
msgstr ""
"Napomena: Ne jamčimo da će ovaj alat ispravno funkcionirati na vašem "
"serveru. Korištenjem ovog alata preuzimate sve rizike i odgovornosti za "
"eventualne probleme."

#: classes/settings/page-permalinks.php:50
msgid "Backup your database before using this tool."
msgstr ""
"Napravite sigurnosnu kopiju svoje baze podataka prije korištenja ovog alata."

