#. Description of the plugin/theme
msgid ""
"All-in-one Cyrillic to Latin transliteration plugin for WordPress. Supports "
"Slavic, Arabic, Greek, and Central Asian scripts."
msgstr ""
"Sve-u-jedan dodatak za WordPress za transliteraciju s ćirilice na latinicu. "
"Podržava slavenske, arapske, grčke i srednjoazijske pisma."

#. Author of the plugin/theme
